{"title":"专升本英语","uid":"e2da92db1d53886d7a5862c5351a8470","slug":"升本/英语/专升本英语","date":"2023-09-20T00:30:00.000Z","updated":"2023-09-23T06:12:30.144Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/升本/英语/专升本英语.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/cover/7.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"专升本英语\"><a href=\"#专升本英语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"专升本英语\"></a>专升本英语</h1><h2 id=\"名词\"><a href=\"#名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"名词\"></a>名词</h2><h3 id=\"可数名词\"><a href=\"#可数名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可数名词\"></a>可数名词</h3><p>个体名词（可数）：表示人或事物的个体名称</p>\n<ul>\n<li>city</li>\n<li>panda</li>\n<li>chair</li>\n<li>hospital</li>\n<li>nurse</li>\n<li>cup</li>\n<li>cat</li>\n</ul>\n<p>集体名词（可数）：表示一群人或一些事物的总称</p>\n<ul>\n<li>public</li>\n<li>people</li>\n<li>class</li>\n<li>family</li>\n<li>police</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"不可数名词\"><a href=\"#不可数名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"不可数名词\"></a>不可数名词</h3><p>物资名词（不可数）：表示无法分为个体的物质或材料的名词</p>\n<ul>\n<li>rice</li>\n<li>snow</li>\n<li>steel</li>\n<li>cotton</li>\n<li>corn</li>\n<li>air</li>\n<li>advice</li>\n<li>equipment</li>\n<li>homework</li>\n<li>furniture</li>\n<li>hair</li>\n<li>information</li>\n<li>traffic</li>\n<li>knowledge</li>\n<li>money</li>\n<li>progress</li>\n<li>water</li>\n<li>news</li>\n<li>gas</li>\n<li>meat</li>\n</ul>\n<p>抽象名词（不可数）：表示行为、状态、品质、感情等抽象概念的名词</p>\n<ul>\n<li>courage</li>\n<li>determination</li>\n<li>satisfaction</li>\n<li>happiness</li>\n<li>success</li>\n<li>love</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"专有名词\"><a href=\"#专有名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"专有名词\"></a>专有名词</h3><p>表示人名、地名、国名：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>London</li>\n<li>Tom</li>\n<li>the Great Wall</li>\n<li>Asia</li>\n</ul>\n<p>表示书名、电影名、各种标语：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spider Man</li>\n</ul>\n<p>表示机构、组织、团体：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>UNESCO</li>\n<li>Beijing University</li>\n</ul>\n<p>表示月份、星期、节日：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Monday</li>\n<li>National day</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"复数\"><a href=\"#复数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"复数\"></a>复数</h3><p>前提是可数名词，才有单复数形式。</p>\n<h4 id=\"元音字母的变化\"><a href=\"#元音字母的变化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"元音字母的变化\"></a>元音字母的变化</h4><ul>\n<li>goose - geese</li>\n<li>mouse - mice</li>\n<li>tooth - teeth</li>\n<li>man - men</li>\n<li>woman - women</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"单复同型\"><a href=\"#单复同型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"单复同型\"></a><strong>单复同型</strong></h4><ul>\n<li>fish</li>\n<li>deer</li>\n<li>sheep</li>\n<li>means</li>\n<li>police</li>\n<li>cattle</li>\n<li>poultry</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"只有复数形式\"><a href=\"#只有复数形式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"只有复数形式\"></a><strong>只有复数形式</strong></h4><ul>\n<li>trousers</li>\n<li>clothes</li>\n<li>glasses</li>\n<li>arms</li>\n<li>remains</li>\n<li>savings</li>\n<li>earnings</li>\n<li>goods</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>一般在名词结尾加-s 在清辅音后读/s/、在浊辅音盒元音后读/z</strong>/：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>exercise - exercises</li>\n<li>desk - desks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以s、x、ch、sh结尾的名词加-es，读/i</strong>/：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>watch - watches</li>\n<li>box📦 - boxes</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以辅音字母 加  y 结尾的名词， 去-y改-i加-es</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>factory - factories</li>\n<li>lady - ladies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以f或者fe结尾的词，一般吧f或fe改v加-es</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>wolf🐺 - wolves</li>\n<li>knife🔪 - knives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以o结尾的可数名词，有生命点加-es、无生命的加-s （黑人英雄爱吃西红柿和土豆🥔）</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>potato🥔 - potatoes</li>\n<li>piano🎹 - pianos</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"复数不规则变化\"><a href=\"#复数不规则变化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"复数不规则变化\"></a>复数不规则变化</h4><ul>\n<li>medium - media</li>\n<li>phenomenon - phenomena</li>\n<li>criterion - criteria</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"特殊情况\"><a href=\"#特殊情况\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特殊情况\"></a>特殊情况</h4><ul>\n<li>child - children</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"复合名词\"><a href=\"#复合名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"复合名词\"></a>复合名词</h3><p>两个或者两个以上的词连接在一起构成的名词：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>passer-by</li>\n<li>brother-in-law</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"复合名词的复数\"><a href=\"#复合名词的复数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"复合名词的复数\"></a>复合名词的复数</h4><p><strong>通常复数加在其所包含的主体词上</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>son-in-law - sons-in-law</li>\n<li>passer-by - passers-by</li>\n<li>editor-in-chief - editors-in-chief</li>\n<li>shoe-maker - shoe-makers</li>\n<li>tooth-brush - tooth - brushes</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>复合名词中没有主体名词时，在最后一个名词后加-s</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>grown-up - grown-ups</li>\n<li>go-between - go-betweens</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>数词加名词做定语时，名词要用单数</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>a two-thousand-word letter</li>\n<li>a ten-mile walk</li>\n<li>a hundred-year plan</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以man和woman构成的合成词变复数是，将man和woman变复数</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>fireman - firemen</li>\n<li>chairwoman - chairwomen</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>以man和woman修饰别的主体词，这两个词要连同主体词一起进行变化</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Man-servant - men-servants</li>\n<li>woman doctor - women doctors</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"物质名词\"><a href=\"#物质名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"物质名词\"></a>物质名词</h3><p>表示不具备确定形状和大小的个体的物质：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>water</li>\n<li>snow</li>\n<li>sunshine</li>\n<li>hair</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"抽象名词\"><a href=\"#抽象名词\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"抽象名词\"></a>抽象名词</h3><p>表示动作，状态，品质或其他抽象概念：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hope</li>\n<li>health</li>\n<li>love</li>\n<li>weather</li>\n<li>labor</li>\n<li>friendship</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"英语虐我千百遍，我待英语如初恋...","permalink":"/post/升本/英语/专升本英语","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"升本","slug":"升本","count":3,"path":"api/categories/升本.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"英语","slug":"英语","count":5,"path":"api/tags/英语.json"},{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":13,"path":"api/tags/笔记.json"},{"name":"升本","slug":"升本","count":3,"path":"api/tags/升本.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%93%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">专升本英语</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">名词</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">可数名词</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">不可数名词</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%93%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\"